This directory contains warning logs captured from successive macOS builds of BES and
its test suite.

The builds used the standard developer-mode autotools configuration:

    autoreconf --force --install --verbose
    ./configure --prefix="$prefix" --with-dependencies="$prefix/deps" --enable-developer
    make
    make check

The files are checked in intentionally as temporary files since the warning cleanup spans 
multiple tickets. 

File names record cleanup iterations. Files with "-check" contain warnings or
diagnostics observed while running the test suite; the others come from build
output.

When the persistent-warning cleanup is complete, summarize the remaining findings
in a report or ticket, then remove this directory.
